  "texts": [
    "The integration of HSI with emerging technologies like IoT (Internet of Things) and blockchain could revolutionise food supply chain management.",
    "The methodology adopted for this review is anchored in the PRISMA (Preferred Reporting Items for Systematic Reviews and Meta-Analyses) framework, as per Page et al., 2021. Our systematic literature search, conducted up to 27 November 2023, aimed to rigorously select articles for review.",
    "We utilised keywords such as 'HIS', 'deep learning', 'machine learning', 'food technology', 'image processing' and 'computer vision' in our search strategy.",
    "Primary databases included Web of Science, Scopus and Google Scholar, ensuring a comprehensive and accurate yield of relevant studies.",
    "All sourced articles underwent an initial screening, focusing on relevance to HSI, deep learning and food technology."
